  "remarks": "\nAZU INTERNATIONAL LTD STI is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 as it is or has been involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty, or independence of Ukraine, by providing goods or technology, specifically, computer components that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n",
